                            <li><a href="#" class="py-2 d-block">服務條款</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md">
                    <div class="ftco-footer-widget mb-4 ml-md-5">
                        <h2 class="ftco-heading-2"><big>顧客權益</big></h2>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li><a href="#" class="py-2 d-block">聯絡我們</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="py-2 d-block">常見Q&A</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="py-2 d-block">防詐騙宣導</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#" class="py-2 d-block">退換貨說明</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="ftco-footer-widget mb-4">
                        <h2 class="ftco-heading-2"><big>企業合作</big></h2>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <ul class="list-unstyled mr-l-5 pr-l-3 mr-4">
                                <li><a href="#" class="py-2 d-block">招商專區</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#" class="py-2 d-block">媒體聯繫</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md">
                    <div class="ftco-footer-widget mb-4">
                        <h2 class="ftco-heading-2"><big>關注我們</big></h2>
                        <div class="block-23 mb-3">
                            <ul class="ftco-footer-social list-unstyled float-md-left float-lft mt-5">
                                <li class="ftco-animate"><a href="#"><span class="icon-twitter"></span></a></li>
                                <li class="ftco-animate"><a href="#"><span class="icon-facebook"></span></a></li>
                                <li class="ftco-animate"><a href="#"><span class="icon-instagram"></span></a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/static/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/static/js/jquery-migrate-3.0.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/static/js/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/static/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/static/js/jquery.easing.1.3.js"></script>
